{"tid":763333,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（FF)其實嗚仔早期應該交俾凱，而唔係卡卡西","createTime":"2018-08-01T04:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T15:11:59.000Z","uid":166295,"like":94,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef01bb70bc529d6b408c7cc914ce569ea002536","tid":763333,"uid":166295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"卡卡西個撚樣早期淨係掛住理Mk佐，連絕技雷切都教埋俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而乜春都無教俾港女櫻同嗚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卡卡西都話過Mk佐同佢好似，一樣都係天才同孤狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  早期完全漠視嗚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反凱班重視團隊合作，而且凱有教無類。天資強如寧次弱如小李凱都重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且性格上嗚門同凱好夾，凱個種青春熱血嗚門應該好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗚門本身就係好努力嘅人，應該會跟著凱不斷特訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算開唔到八門，如果有小李咁嘅速度同體術加埋多重影分身都已經夠屌打MK佐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲d學嘅螺旋丸，可以話係百發百中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果早期交嗚仔俾凱教，一早屌打MK佐，做埋上忍都唔出奇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 交俾卡卡西浪費哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459904c124e8e19891a76d2299467599b5718cb1","tid":763333,"uid":166295,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"用螺旋丸推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f5b0382d895b725e298f6108b0e3864e877c87","tid":763333,"uid":166295,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0ca66c72e04abd77ad6788835ecc0e36851694","tid":763333,"uid":166295,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"連登火影撚係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaf880611f1540a62ef743b944ab1f68b81dfe8","tid":763333,"uid":85235,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"仲衰, 凱唔識屬性轉換, 唔識教嗚門手裹劍.<br />\n同埋其實邊個做老師影響都唔係太大, 好快都會走個自來也出嚟捉走嗚門"},{"pid":"88d8c8c750c2eddfb0b76104703236572a3af5dc","tid":763333,"uid":47268,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"如果牙嗚遇唔到自來也應該乜都唔係"},{"pid":"cd72f7f3b46f7aeaeecb560f3c9482cb0f63afbb","tid":763333,"uid":166295,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"aaaf880611f1540a62ef743b944ab1f68b81dfe8","tid":763333,"uid":85235,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"仲衰, 凱唔識屬性轉換, 唔識教嗚門手裹劍.<br />\n同埋其實邊個做老師影響都唔係太大, 好快都會走個自來也出嚟捉走嗚門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"去到疾風傳緊係交翻俾大和同卡卡西，此終要練新術同學用九尾查克拉。但係疾傳前跟凱，個基礎應該會好好多。"},{"pid":"178fb500a12f14e6cee55348fc06863d845a509f","tid":763333,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"換寧次去第7班？<br />\n白眼寫輪眼世仇遲早打大交"},{"pid":"e447afa3b7d5b4c3dd7e40ce528a500cb63618a3","tid":763333,"uid":166295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88d8c8c750c2eddfb0b76104703236572a3af5dc","tid":763333,"uid":47268,"like"